snippet.title: 9-1-1: The Real Reason Why These Actors Leave The Show |⭐ OSSA
snippet.description:
The 9-1-1 series gave us over 5 seasons where 9-1-1 actors hit us with their perfect performance in each episode, that is why we all love this show its cast. However, the show loves to surprise the viewers not only with the plot but also with unexpected changes in the cast, so we decided to take a closer look behind the scenes of the 9-1-1 show and to talk about new hires and about cast members who almost left the show.

Ossa is going to tell you all the unbelievable truth about unexpected 9-1-1 cast changes, so you will know why Connie Britton (Abby Clark), Jennifer Love-Hewitt (Maddie Kendall), Rockmond Dunbar (Michael Grant) left the show, and of course, we won’t forget to talk about new hires: Vanessa Estelle Williams (Claudette Collins), and about actors who almost left the show: Rayan Guzman (Eddie Diaz), Aisha Hinds (Henrieta Willson). What is the reason why Connie Britton, who performed our beloved Abby Clark, left the 9-1-1 after one short season of the show? 

Who did make Jennifer Love-Hewitt, whose 9-9-1 character Maddie Kendall was supposed to replace Abby Clark, leave the 9-9-1 series, and shall we hope to see her return or Vanessa Estelle Williams will replace her forever with her character Claudette Collins? What was the reason for firing Rockmond Dunbar, who act the role of Michael Grant, and what was the fans’ reaction to it? Why you should expect to see Rayan Guzman in the new season of the 9-9-1 series, although we saw his character Eddie Diaz had been hurt at the end of the previous season? What does Aisha Hinds (Henrieta Willson) think about her character’s plotline?

Watch our OSSA’m video to find out everything about unbelievable truth about unexpected 9-1-1 cast changes. We are going to tell you the 9-1-1 cast’s opinion on this and we won’t forget to tell you what showrunner Tim Minear and the creator Rayan Murphy think about it. So get ready course we are going to start!

02:40 - Jennifer Love-Hewitt as Maddie Kendall
04:34 - Rockmond Dunbar as Michael Grant
06:22 - Vanessa Estelle Williams as Claudette Collins
07:10 - Ryan Guzman as Eddie Diaz
08:45 - Aisha Hinds as Henrietta Wilson
